UGREEN Headphone Mic Splitter Adapter 3.5mm 2 Male to Female TRRS Headphone to PC Adapter

The UGREEN 3.5mm stereo y-splitter cable allows you to easily connect your stereo headset & Mic to a PC audio port and mic port at the same time. enabling you to add a mono microphone input, as well as a stereo output to your PC or Laptop, through a single 3.5mm audio port. It works with all PC Applications - Skype, MSN Messenger, Yahoo, Google Voice, etc.

Perfect Solution For Gaming

  • This cable is mainly used for CTIA standard Mobile headsets or earphones, for example, it can be used for turtle beach Z11, M5Ti, M5, M3, px24, RECON 100, Star Wars headset, Ear Force Recon 50, Ear Force Recon 50P, Ear Force Recon 50X.
  • Compatible with various laptops that have a separate mic and audio ports such as the HP ProBook 450 G1 / Lenovo Thinkpad T400

Warm Tips

  • To ensure proper hardware detection, we recommend that the external headset be plugged into this adapter first, before the adapter is connected to the computer or mobile device.
  • Only compatible with CTIA standard Android headphones, Not compatible with CTIA standard Apple Earbuds.
  • Because of the different connector pin connection, this headphone mic cable is not recommended for Apple original earphone and Beats headphone.

- UGREEN 3.5mm stereo y-splitter cable allows you to easily connect your stereo headset & Mic to a PC audio port and mic port at the same time, enabling you to add a mono microphone input as well as a stereo output to your PC or Laptop through a single 3.5mm audio port.

Special Features

- 24K Gold Plated for better sound quality and less loss

- Input: 3.5mm 4-position female(TRRS) for headset or earphone

- Output 1: 3.5mm 3-position(TRS) male for Audio Jack on your PC/Laptop

- Output 2: 3.5mm 3-position(TRS) male for Mic Jack on your PC/Laptop

- Flexible cable length: 20cm

In the Box

UGREEN 3.5mm Female to Dual Male Headphone Splitter Cable x 1

Plug and Play

  • One for Headphone Jack on your PC/Laptop, the other for Mic Jack on your PC/Laptop
  • UGREEN mic headphone splitter splits 1 headset (support audio & microphone) jack into a separate headphone and microphone jack.

Durable and Flexible Cord

Durable shielding with nylon braided significantly enhances the flexibility and durability for a longer lifespan.

Exceptional Stereo Sound

Made of Oxygen-free copper, ensuring high fidelity sound quality and without current noise.

      Product description

      Color:Black


      The UGREEN 3.5mm stereo y-splitter cable allows you to easily connect your stereo headset & Mic to a PC audio port and mic port at the same time.enabling you to add a mono microphone input, as well as a stereo output to your PC or Laptop, through a single 3.5mm audio port. It works with all PC Applications - Skype, MSN Mesenger, Yahoo, Google Voice etc.

      Difference with Other Brands:
      Comparing with PVC spliiters from other brands,this one is in shielding and much more durable with Aluminum case.

      Features:
      -24K Gold Plated for better sound quality and less loss
      -Input: 3.5mm 4-position female for headset or earphone
      -Output 1: 3.5mm 3-positiion male for Headphone Jack on your PC/Laptop
      -Output 2: 3.5mm 3-position male for Mic Jack on your PC/Laptop
      - Copper provide maximum's conductivity and durability.
      -Flexible cable length 20cm

      Innovative Audio Ports
      While some laptops like Dell feature only a single (4-position) 3.5mm audio port to support both audio input and output, this innovative headset splitter adapter breaks the audio port out into two distinct ports - one that can be used for a microphone input connection, and the other for connecting external (output) speakers

      Warm Tips:
      -To ensure proper hardware detection, we recommend that the external headset be plugged into the adapter first, before the adapter is connected to the computer or mobile device.
      -Only compatible with CTIA standard Android headphones, do NOT compatible with CTIA standard Apple Earbuds.
      -Not compatible with Beats headphone, Bose Earbuds and Apple headphone.

      In The Box:
      UGREEN 3.5mm female to 2 male Headphone Mic Audio Y Splitter Cable
